Unfortunately, in this case, the spacecraft are identical to Starcraft 
battle-cruisers in almost every detail,and at 0:51-0:52, the larger 
spacecraft does a little wiggle-dance that is almost impossible for 
something so large to do at that speed.
Also, at such close proximity there would've been a lot of screaming and 
pannicking, and snow would have been blowing around more violently.
If such an incident had REALLY occurred, there would've been no-one left to 
tell the tale, or to send the video.
Overall, however, the graphics are very impressive.
Kudos .﻿
